highlights.text: “Hier Mag Alles” by Donnie and Marco Schuitmaker has been on Top Songs Netherlands the longest, at 603 days straight.
“Hoe Het Is” by Roxy Dekker, Idaly, and Ronnie Flex is the highest new entry on Top Songs Netherlands at #1.
Roxy Dekker has the most spots on Top Songs Netherlands. “Hoe Het Is” is the highest at #1.
“Vannacht Slaap Jij Bij Mij” by Afro Bros, John West, Billy Dans, and Monq is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Netherlands, up 58 spots at #114.
